data.description: Welcome home to this charming home nestled on 3.21 private acres.  This home features 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths on the main floor and 2 bedrooms,1 full bath downstairs.  The living room features a fireplace.  The newly rebuilt deck is perfect for entertaining, or sitting and enjoying a cup of coffee overlooking your backyard.  The newly added detached garage features 12 ft. ceilings, 3 10x10 roll up docks, and steel reinforced flooring.  No HOA or covenants.  This home won't last.  Don't miss the opportunity to experience the serenity and comfort this home has to offer.This home will need TLC, but you LOVE calling this house, home.
